rges, Fees Or Premiums For Credit Insurance Or Auto Club Memberships Shall Not Be Included In The Calculation Of The Finance Charge; To Amend Section 75-17-25, Mississippi Code Of 1972, To Conform To The Preceding Provision; And For Related Purposes.</description><committee/><history><step><date>2013-01-21</date><action>Referred To Business and Financial Institutions</action><chamber>S</chamber><chamber_id>58</chamber_id><importance>1</importance></step><step><date>2013-01-29</date><action>Title Suff Do Pass Comm Sub</action><chamber>S</chamber><chamber_id>58</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></step><step><date>2013-02-06</date><action>Committee Substitute Adopted</action><chamber>S</chamber><chamber_id>58</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></step><step><date>2013-02-06</date><action>Amended</action><chamber>S</chamber><chamber_id>58</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></step><step><date>2013-02-06</date><action>Passed As Amended</action><chamber>S</chamber><chamber_id>58</chamber_id><importance>1</importance></step><step><date>2013-02-11</date><action>Transmitted To House</action><chamber>S</chamber><chamber_id>58</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></step><step><date>2013-02-20</date><action>Referred To Banking and Financial Services</action><chamber>H</chamber><chamber_id>57</chamber_id><importance>1</importance></step><step><date>2013-03-01</date><action>Title Suff Do Pass As Amended</action><chamber>H</chamber><chamber_id>57</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></step><step><date>2013-03-05</date><action>Tabled Subject To Call</action><chamber>H</chamber><chamber_id>57</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></step><step><date>2013-03-06</date><action>Amended</action><chamber>H</chamber><chamber_id>57</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></step><step><date>2013-03-06</date><action>Point of Order Raised</action><chamber>H</chamber><chamber_id>57</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></step><step><date>2013-03-06</date><action>Set Aside-Pend Ruling of 